                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 657.119/384b</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Ambassador in Great Britain</hi> (<persName
                        corresp="frus1918Supp01v01#p_PWH1" type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Page</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-03-07T15:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 7, 1918—3 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>6789. For <persName corresp="frus1918Supp01v01#p_SLP1">Sheldon</persName> [from
                    War Trade Board]:</p>
                <p>No. 170. The following schedules of articles showing the annual import
                    requirements of Norway, are the schedules mentioned in cabled agreement of March
                    2 (quantities are in metric tons): <table cols="3" rows="53">
                        <row>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell>A.</cell>
                            <cell>Foodstuffs and fodder:</cell>
                            <cell/>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell>Bread grains, including rice</cell>
                            <cell role="num">300,000</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell>Oil cake</cell>
                            <cell role="num">25,000</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell>Grains</cell>
                            <cell role="num">60,000</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell>Starches</cell>
                            <cell role="num">1,000</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell>Cocoa</cell>
                            <cell role="num">1,400</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell>Coffee</cell>
                            <cell role="num">14,500</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell>Tea</cell>
                            <cell role="num">160</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell>Sauces and pickles</cell>
                            <cell role="num">80</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell>Sirup</cell>
                            <cell role="num">5,000</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell>Spices</cell>
                            <cell role="num">382</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell>Fruit, dried</cell>
                            <cell role="num">4,000</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell>Fruit, fresh</cell>
                            <cell role="num">6,000</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell>Sugar</cell>
                            <cell role="num">50,000</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell>Pork and beef</cell>
                            <cell role="num">10,000</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell>Wines</cell>
                            <cell role="num">2,000</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell>B.</cell>
                            <cell>Oils and fats, etc.:</cell>
                            <cell/>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell>Vegetable and animal oils</cell>
                            <cell role="num">10,000</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell>Oil seeds</cell>
                            <cell role="num">20,000</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell/>
